		<body>
			<head>
				<title>
					<app>
						<lem wit="#Transcription">Brief an ungenannte Sanktimonialen zur Assumptio Marias</lem>
						<rdg wit="#Translation"></rdg>
					</app>
				</title>
			</head>
			<div n="1">
				<p n="1">
					<s>
						<app>
							<lem wit="#Transcription">Frater Gerhohus fratrum Richerspergensium servus dilectis in Christo sororibus.</lem>
							<rdg wit="#Translation"></rdg>
						</app>
					</s>
					<s>
						<app>
							<lem wit="#Transcription">Vigilare et adventum sponsi observare.</lem>
							<rdg wit="#Translation"></rdg>
						</app>
					</s>
				</p>
				<p n="2">
					<s>
						<app>
							<lem wit="#Transcription">Scribenti mihi ad feminas Deo devotas trium feminarum nunc occurit memoria, quas varia descriptione sapientia notabiles demonstrat.</lem>
							<rdg wit="#Translation"></rdg>
						</app>
					</s>
					<s>
						<app>
							<lem wit="#Transcription">Preponitur enim una cavenda, secunda imitanda, tercia miranda.</lem>
							<rdg wit="#Translation"></rdg>
						</app>
					</s>
					<s>
						<app>
							<lem wit="#Transcription">An non vitanda seu cavenda est illa, que in principio parabolarum Salemonis describitur garrula et vaga quietis impatiens (37), an non videtur imitanda, quam in earundem fine parabolarum scribit sapientia sapientem, pariter et fortem (38).
								<note type="critical" ancored="true">
									<p>(37) Prov 7, 10-11.</p>
									<p>(38)Vgl. Prov 31, 10-31.</p>
								</note>
							</lem>
							<rdg wit="#Translation"></rdg>
						</app>
					</s>
					<s>
						<app>
							<lem wit="#Transcription">Nam ut in sexu fagili tam raram quam preclaram ostenderet fortitudinem dicit: Mulierem fortem quis inveniet? (39)
								<note type="critical" anchored="true">
									<p>Prov 31, 10.</p>
								</note>
							</lem>
							<rdg wit="#Translation"></rdg>
						</app>
					</s>

					<s>
						<app>
							<lem wit="#Transcription">Item: Quesivit lanam et linum et operata est consilio manuum suarum.
								<note type="critical" anchored="true">
									<p></p>
								</note>
							</lem>
							<rdg wit="#Translation"></rdg>
						</app>
					</s>


				</p>
